<h2>All of the membership codes</h2>

<p>Use this list to import into Eventbrite. To find out more, see the <a href="https://github.com/james/london-decom-membership#codes">README</a></p>

<p><%= link_to "Download codes CSV", admin_membership_codes_path(format: :csv) %></p>

<p><%= MembershipCode.taken.count %> codes have been assigned</p>
<p>There are <%= MembershipCode.available.count %> available codes left</p>

<h2>Pre generate some more membership codes</h2>
<%= bootstrap_form_tag url: admin_membership_codes_path do |f| %>
  <%= f.number_field :number, label: 'Number of codes to generate' %>
  <%= f.submit 'Create' %>
<% end %>
